room_title: Escape room "Submerged" by North Texas Escape Rooms in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_description: Your submarine crew has been tasked with a top-secret mission but the Captain has become incapacitated. Break into the Captain's quarters, find the classified coordinates and use them to guide the vessel to your final destination. You must hurry! You have 60 minutes before the submarine's oxygen level reaches critical. Can you handle the pressure and find a way out, or will you be submerged?
